# Build directories
build/
builds/
cmake-build-*/
out/
dist/
# Intentionally NOT ignoring *.framework/ or *.xcframework/ — we track
# the prebuilt XCFrameworks at flutter/{ios,macos}/Frameworks/ and they
# must survive git clone for downstream consumers (flutter-news podspec
# uses :git source + vendored_frameworks path inside the cloned repo).
# Previously `*.xcframework/` here caused CocoaPods to drop the
# vendored framework from Pods/EdgeVedaCore/ on fresh pod install,
# breaking iOS and watchOS builds (Sentry 7414461351 family).
# Only ignore XCFrameworks under transient build/ outputs:
build/**/*.xcframework/
build/**/*.framework/
*.aar

